parameters: Iburu: "Ah... Are all the arrangements in place?"
Soldier: "Yes... there's no problem with that... However..."

Iburu: "I understand... I'll cede the mining rights to you... It's better
than the village being wiped out."
Soldier: "That's true... But how have you been hiding it until now?"
Iburu: "I've been making various preparations for a time like this..."
Soldier: "Like pretending to be a drunkard?"

Iburu: "No, no... I really do like alcohol. More importantly, are you sure
you're prepared for the hypnotic magic...?"

Soldier: "Ah, it's fine. General Tros has been sounding the alarm. We've
been preparing for a long time."
Soldier: "I would have done it even without being asked..."
